                            <comment id="12995577" author="gmazza" created="Wed, 16 Feb 2011 23:24:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Aaron, there seems something wrong with your patch, the very last &quot;writer.writeStartElement(defaultPrefix, &quot;Fault&quot;, ns);&quot; at the bottom (carried over from the original code) would need to be nuked, correct?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
